name: Daoist Robe - 天師派道袍
description:
--Version 2 adjusted the Lora Training Parameters for better effects--
Lora trained based on 10 distinct 512x768 Daoist Robe (DaoPao) (天師派道袍) Photos based on MajicMix Realistic v4 Model.


For best results, you may follow the setting

Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras

Steps: 20+

Lora Weight: 0.4-0.7

Model: MajicMix Series (e.g. MajicMix realistic v2/v4/v5/Lux/Sombre) for Realistic pictures

These are the possible prompts - 以下是你都可以用的Trigger提示詞:

Must (必須): Daoist_robe

You can adjust the color of the robe using the following prompt - 你可以修改道袍的顏色:

  • e.g. red daoist_robe, black daoist_robe, etc

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description: Modified the Base Model that was trained on for more flexibility. Can adapt to different posture
